      <title>印度证券交易所将加强对中小企业上市的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/indian-bourse-said-to-push-for-tighter-scrutiny-of-sme-listings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度证券交易所运营商孟买证券交易所 (BSE Ltd.) 已要求银行家加强对小公司首次公开募股申请的监督，此前该交易所发现近期一些交易的备案文件存在差异。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/indian-bourse-said-to-push-for-tighter-scrutiny-of-sme-listings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 02:22:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
