      <title>中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1420 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-weighs-injecting-142-billion-of-capital-into-top-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国正考虑向其最大的国有银行注入高达 1 万亿元人民币（1420 亿美元）的资本，以增强其支持陷入困境的经济的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-weighs-injecting-142-billion-of-capital-into-top-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
